item.title: No title
item.description: Tier 1 Entrepreneur visa is ideal for entrepreneurs looking to start a business in the UK from the scratch, takeover or invest in already existing company and being actively involved in the running of it. One of the major requirements for this visa is the access to at least £200,000 or £50,000 (for certain applicants) held in a regulated financial institution.
